OL,3,CRogue traders made pensioner buy them
OL,4,Cgold bracelet worth thousands
OL,6,FChislett and Lee, accompanied by one
OL,7,Fother labourer, cold called at the
OL,8,Fhome of a man living in Falmouth, in
OL,9,FJanuary 2024. The elderly man was
OL,10,Fliving with dementia.
OL,12,FThey told him his roof needed
OL,13,Fcleaning, but after they erected
OL,14,Fladders and went up on the roof they
OL,15,Fclaimed that it needed fixing as well.
OL,17,FThey gave him a verbal quote of
OL,18,F#5,000, with no paperwork and said the
OL,19,Fmoney needed to be paid upfront.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
