OL,3,CRogue traders made pensioner buy them
OL,4,Cgold bracelet worth thousands
OL,6,FA customer called to enquire about
OL,7,Fhaving some hedges cut back and was
OL,8,Fpersuaded to get the work done.
OL,9,FChislett and Lee turned up at the
OL,10,Fproperty shortly after and cut back
OL,11,Fthe bushes.
OL,13,FThey did not provide any paperwork or
OL,14,Fgive any form of cancellation period.
OL,15,FUpon completion of the work, they
OL,16,Fdemanded #300 in payment.
OL,18,FThe customer felt confused and
OL,19,Fpressured by the situation. Chislett
OL,20,Fand Lee asked him to give them his
OL,21,Fbank card and PIN, which he did.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
