OL,3,CRogue traders made pensioner buy them
OL,4,Cgold bracelet worth thousands
OL,6,FThe two men took the card to a local
OL,7,Fsupermarket and withdrew #300.
OL,8,FHowever, when they came back, they
OL,9,Fdemanded a further #1,000.
OL,11,FPanicked, the victim called his father
OL,12,Fwho bank transferred the money and
OL,13,FChislett and Lee left. Unknown to them
OL,14,Fat the time, the payment was blocked
OL,15,Fby the bank.
OL,17,FTraders plead guilty to attempted
OL,18,Ftheft and fraud charges
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
