OL,3,CRogue traders made pensioner buy them
OL,4,Cgold bracelet worth thousands
OL,6,FOn 3 April 2025, Chislett and Lee,
OL,7,Fboth of Wheal Jewel, Redruth, were
OL,8,Fsentenced to two years in prison at
OL,9,FTruro Crown Court.
OL,11,FThey had each pleaded guilty to three
OL,12,Fcharges of attempted theft and two
OL,13,Fcharges of fraud at a previous hearing.
OL,15,FGary Webster, trading standards group
OL,16,Fleader at Cornwall Council, said:
OL,17,F"These incidents are truly shocking
OL,18,Fexamples of how some of the most
OL,19,Fvulnerable people in our community can
OL,20,Fbe exploited for financial gain.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
