OL,3,CRogue traders made pensioner buy them
OL,4,Cgold bracelet worth thousands
OL,6,F"It is clear that both Chislett and
OL,7,FLee operated solely with the intent of
OL,8,Fidentifying the most vulnerable
OL,9,Fconsumers, with little interest in
OL,10,Fcompleting any meaningful work.
OL,12,F"Thankfully on this occasion the
OL,13,Fpolice and Trading Standards were
OL,14,Falerted to these incidents; however,
OL,15,Fwe know that there are many more that
OL,16,Fare not reported.
OL,18,F"It is vital that communities are
OL,19,Fvigilant and look out for friends and
OL,20,Fneighbours and report any suspicious
OL,21,Factivity."
